{"tid":2084273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發現老翁跌落渠向人求救・好心貓獲警方贈貓糧","createTime":"2020-06-29T07:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T09:27:24.000Z","uid":118346,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"968895078a7b967ad4073c01ee189d0a506f6653","tid":2084273,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:17:16.000Z","msg":"日本富山市日前一老翁因失足不慎掉到水渠，幸好在附近散步的女士因看到貓貓Coco緊盯水渠，並不停喵喵叫吸引她的注意力，才發現老翁墜渠，與途人展開救援讓老人得救。富山南警署向5位途人頒發感謝狀，並表彰最大功臣Coco，送上貓糧一包。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/6/1593333354_oO-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F6%2F1593333354_oO-1280w.jpg&h=eeb15cec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2d0dd6741b553343e9ad1755deb28c5a7266718","tid":2084273,"uid":9193,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:18:07.000Z","msg":"點解係送貓糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"887c7b46ca026649180166f9a4abd04f1c0ab788","tid":2084273,"uid":182334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:19:18.000Z","msg":"屌標提黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0ce515b4f725cb71ea2a011dd6d2e1339c3c40","tid":2084273,"uid":71657,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"f2d0dd6741b553343e9ad1755deb28c5a7266718","tid":2084273,"uid":9193,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:18:07.000Z","msg":"點解係送貓糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:19:39.000Z","msg":"因為係貓貓發現<br />\n而且可以做到公關效果"},{"pid":"18e7208a8518a82eb249db25a51a1160d9f14858","tid":2084273,"uid":178976,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f2d0dd6741b553343e9ad1755deb28c5a7266718","tid":2084273,"uid":9193,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":